title: #100daysofCode
content:
Two Main Rules
Code minimum an hour every day for the next 100 days.
Tweet your progress every day with the #100DaysOfCode hashtag.

Creating new Habits!

title: Road towards Mastery
content:
The principle holds that 10,000 hours of "deliberate practice" are needed to become world-class in any field. When psychologists talk about deliberate practice, they mean practicing in a way that pushes your skill set as much as possible. 

Im on my way <3 Coding <3

title: Why learning coding is important?
content:
Nowadays with everything being electronic, everything needs to be programmed! 

From computers, to cars, machines, or anything else it most likely requires programming!

So as a result, demand for coders keeps increasing year by year, due to all these technological advances!
